<section class="about-section" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-story">
      <div class="about-story__text">
        <span class="section-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <h2 id="story-heading" class="about-story__title">The Story</h2>
        <p>
          Every developer knows the drill. You need to quickly format some JSON, decode a JWT, or test a regex, and you end up on a site that throws five pop-ups at you before you even see the tool. That's the problem Value.Codes was built to solve.
        </p>
        <p>
          What started as a personal collection of bookmarked utilities turned into a proper platform. The goal was straightforward: build the tools I actually use day to day, make them fast, make them clean, and make them free. No accounts, no paywalls, no friction.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, Value.Codes is home to over 10 browser-based developer tools, an online compiler that supports 19 languages, curated developer resources, and a growing blog covering programming, AI, and web development trends.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-story__visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="about-code-card">
          <div class="about-code-card__dots">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
          </div>
          <pre class="about-code-card__code"><code><span class="code-keyword">const</span> mission = {
  tools:   <span class="code-string">"free &amp; browser-based"</span>,
  friction: <span class="code-number">0</span>,
  signups:  <span class="code-bool">false</span>,
  ads:      <span class="code-string">"non-intrusive"</span>,
  purpose:  <span class="code-string">"for developers"</span>
};</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section about-section--surface" aria-labelledby="mission-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section__header">
      <span class="section-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
      <h2 id="mission-heading">Our Mission</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-values-grid">
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Speed First</h3>
        <p>Every tool loads fast. No heavyweight frameworks bloating the page. No spinner while you wait. Your time is the most valuable resource.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Privacy by Design</h3>
        <p>All processing happens in your browser. Sensitive data such as API keys, JWTs, and code never touches our servers. What you paste stays with you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>No Dark Patterns</h3>
        <p>No forced signups. No misleading download buttons. No fake countdown timers. The tools are the product, not you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Built for Real Work</h3>
        <p>Each tool exists because a developer actually needed it. They are designed around real workflows, not theoretical use cases.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Community Driven</h3>
        <p>We listen to feedback, fix bugs fast, and regularly add new tools based on what developers actually request.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-value-card">
        <h3>Always Improving</h3>
        <p>Value.Codes is an ongoing project. New tools, better performance, and sharper content. Shipping constantly, not quarterly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

